name: Oracle
queryCode:
SELECT t1.* FROM (SELECT
t1.APPCATEGORY,
t1.CREATEDATE,
t1.CREATEMAN,
t1.ICON,
t1.ICONCSS,
t1.MOBILEAPP,
t1.PERMISSIONTAG,
t1.PSSYSAPPFUNCID,
t1.PSSYSAPPFUNCNAME,
t1.PSSYSTEMAPPID,
t1.PSSYSTEMAPPNAME,
t1.SHOWORDER,
t1.SRFDCID,
t1.SYSTEMID,
t1.TIP,
t1.UPDATEDATE,
t1.UPDATEMAN,
t1.URL,
t1.VIEWPATHPARAMS
FROM IBZPSSYSAPPFUNC t1 
LEFT JOIN IBZPSSYSTEM t11 ON t1.SYSTEMID = t11.PSSYSTEMID 

WHERE 
EXISTS(SELECT * FROM IBZDCSYSTEM t21 
 WHERE 
( t21.SRFDCID =  ${srfsessioncontext('srfdcid','{"defname":"SRFDCID","dename":"SYS_DC_SYSTEM"}')} ) AND
 t11.PSSYSTEMID = t21.SYSTEMID )AND ( t1.SRFDCID =  ${srfsessioncontext('srfdcid','{"defname":"SRFDCID","dename":"SYS_DC_SYSTEM"}')}) )t1 INNER JOIN
(SELECT 
t21.PERMISSIONTAG
,t21.PSSYSTEMID 
FROM IBZPERMISSION t21 
WHERE 
EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM IBZROLE_PERMISSION t22 
LEFT JOIN IBZUSER_ROLE t23 ON t23.SYS_ROLEID = t22.SYS_ROLEID 
WHERE 
t21.SYS_PERMISSIONID = t22.SYS_PERMISSIONID AND t22.ISVALID = 1 AND t23.ISVALID = 1 AND t23.USERID =${srfsessioncontext('srfpersonid','{"defname":"USERID","dename":"IBZEMP"}')} ) 
AND t21.PERMISSIONTYPE='UNIRES') t2 ON t2.PSSYSTEMID=t1.SYSTEMID AND t2.PERMISSIONTAG=t1.PERMISSIONTAG
